  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for xen",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xen fixes the following issues:\n\nSecurity issues fixed:\n\n- CVE-2024-45818: xen: Deadlock in x86 HVM standard VGA handling (bsc#1232622)\n- CVE-2024-45819: xen: libxl leaks data to PVH guests via ACPI tables (bsc#1232624)\n\nNon-security issue fixed:\n\n- Xen host hung at boot up with repeated '(XEN) APIC error on CPU on CPU53: 40(40), Received illegal vector' (bsc#1231046)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
